# Rocq project file for Unification Soundness correctness proofs
#
# Verifies soundness of the Martelli-Montanari unification algorithm
# (unification.rs):
#
#   - MGU soundness: if unify succeeds, the substitution satisfies all equations
#   - Occurs check: failure implies unsatisfiability
#   - Constructor clash: failure implies unsatisfiability
#   - TheoryAlgebra bridge preserves BooleanAlgebra axioms
#
# Model: terms as inductive type with Var, Const, App constructors.
#
# Reference: Martelli & Montanari (1982), Robinson (1965)

-Q theories UnificationProofs

